## Page 25: Online Application `/apply`

### Multi-step form
1. Personal info (name, DOB, nationality, passport)
2. Education background (degree, GPA, school)
3. Destination preferences (country, program, intake)
4. Test scores (IELTS, TOPIK, etc.)
5. Documents upload
6. Review & submit
7. Confirmation with tracking ID

---

